text: Yolandi Du Toit (born 3 June 1985) is a road cyclist from South Africa. She represented her nation at the 2006, 2007 and 2008 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1985 births Category:South African female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
